        <degreeDatas>
            <li>
                <degree>0</degree>
                <label>relaxed</label>
                <description>[PAWN_nameDef] takes life easy and sleeps soundly. Stress rarely gets to [PAWN_objective] and [PAWN_pronoun] generally enjoys whatever [PAWN_pronoun]'s doing, but [PAWN_pronoun]'s not the fastest worker.</description>
